WEBVTT

00:06.000 --> 00:12.074
-= www.OpenSubtitles.org =-

00:59.600 --> 01:03.850
To tell ya the truth,
I never was much for the holidays.

01:03.920 --> 01:06.950
It's been forever
since I'd known a holiday,

01:07.020 --> 01:09.870
since I'd seen my family,

01:09.990 --> 01:14.050
since I'd been with a girl,
since I'd driven a car.

01:14.120 --> 01:17.190
You see, cars are what put me here.

01:17.260 --> 01:20.100
Iron Mountain, maximum security.

01:20.170 --> 01:23.020
I was riding a hard five
for grand theft auto.

01:23.080 --> 01:28.010
Meanwhile, my esteemed raping and murdering
colleagues were up for parole at three.

01:28.070 --> 01:30.380
World works like that sometimes.

01:30.440 --> 01:32.560
All the time in my experience.

01:32.620 --> 01:37.290
That's me, Rudy Duncan,
menace to society, on the left.

01:37.360 --> 01:40.400
The guy on the right's
Nick Cassidy, my best friend.

01:40.460 --> 01:43.020
Back then, we were both looking
at three days to a new start.

01:43.090 --> 01:45.680
That's what ya talk about
inprison.

01:45.740 --> 01:49.930
How you're gonna get it right.
How you'll never make the same mistakes.

01:57.230 --> 01:59.920
We walk outta here, we hit that road,

01:59.990 --> 02:02.060
what's the first thing
you're gonna do ?

02:02.130 --> 02:04.880
Hot chocolate.

02:04.940 --> 02:08.180
- What ?
- That's the first thing I'm gonna do.

02:08.240 --> 02:10.479
I'm gonna go out and get myself
a mug of hot chocolate.

02:10.550 --> 02:12.370
And a piece of pecan pie.

02:12.430 --> 02:15.570
That's right.
A piece of pecan pie.

02:15.640 --> 02:17.650
Yeah.

02:17.710 --> 02:20.630
She's gonna be
out there, man.

02:20.690 --> 02:23.920
She's gonna be
right there waiting.

02:23.990 --> 02:27.450
She got us a motel
on Highway 5.

02:27.500 --> 02:30.770
Lock ourselves in
the whole week,

02:30.840 --> 02:34.260
drinkin' wine,
takin' baths, man.

02:38.350 --> 02:40.220
Yeah.

02:41.880 --> 02:45.210
Nick, all those pictures
she sent ?

02:45.300 --> 02:47.670
You sure that's really her
in the pictures ?

02:47.730 --> 02:50.350
I did hear sometimes these girls
send pictures that's not really them.

02:50.420 --> 02:53.140
It's like their prettier cousin
or somethin' like that.

02:53.210 --> 02:55.440
Why ya gotta say
a thing like that, man ?

02:55.510 --> 02:58.070
- I'm just sayin'...
- Why ya gotta say a thing like that ?

02:58.130 --> 03:02.260
I'm just sayin',
maybe I should take her out.

03:02.330 --> 03:05.370
Spend a day or two with her.
Make sure she's the right girl.

03:05.430 --> 03:09.530
Just a day or two.
Maybe a night or two ?

03:09.600 --> 03:12.980
Whatever it takes. Just make sure
you're gettin' the right merchandise.

03:13.050 --> 03:16.570
- You know ?
- You know what ?

03:16.630 --> 03:19.000
Enjoy your hot chocolate, Rudy.

03:19.060 --> 03:22.490
I think I'll take my chances
with Ashley.

03:23.810 --> 03:26.650
Yeah, I figured.
I figured.

03:29.210 --> 03:34.140
- Hold it up close.
- Pop gate three.

03:34.200 --> 03:36.700
Oh, shit !

03:36.770 --> 03:40.060
- What's up ?
- Alamo's back.

03:40.160 --> 03:43.390
Don't look like he missed the sunlight.

03:43.450 --> 03:45.950
Bro, I'm fucked.

03:46.010 --> 03:48.830
Pincher said he thinks I'm the one
who ratted him out for beating up Creed.

03:48.890 --> 03:51.360
'Cause I was there, he thinks
I'm the reason he ended up in solitar.

03:51.420 --> 03:53.500
Fuck, Rudy.

03:53.570 --> 03:55.450
Move out!

04:04.710 --> 04:06.850
And stop !

04:07.870 --> 04:10.470
Move in !

04:10.520 --> 04:12.390
Listen to this.

04:12.440 --> 04:15.170
"I've made my list
and I've checked it twice.

04:15.230 --> 04:18.750
"As long as you're naughty,
it's gonna be nice.

04:18.820 --> 04:23.910
"All that gets me through the day, is to
close my eyes and imagine holding you,

04:23.970 --> 04:26.460
"kissing you, touching you.

04:26.530 --> 04:30.250
"Because I know I'll feel
at that moment...

04:30.300 --> 04:34.210
I've found the reason
for my whole entire life."

04:34.280 --> 04:36.580
She sounds pretty mature
for 25.

04:36.640 --> 04:39.140
Yeah !

04:39.200 --> 04:41.540
You grow up in Detroit,
you get matured real quick.

04:41.600 --> 04:45.700
Yeah. Either that
or those pictures are ten years old.

04:48.580 --> 04:52.520
Sure as hell don't
make me miss Millie Bobeck.

04:52.580 --> 04:55.590
Guess I owe Millie, though.

04:55.650 --> 04:58.120
Ifl hadn't been
rolling her,

04:58.180 --> 05:00.390
I would've never
ended up here.

05:00.450 --> 05:03.950
Yeah. You hadn't have cracked that guy's head open,
you never would've found true love.

05:04.000 --> 05:06.280
Jealous.

05:06.350 --> 05:10.720
Ya know, Nick, what if
she sees you and, you know,

05:10.790 --> 05:13.380
you just don't do it for her,
you know, I mean physically ?

05:13.450 --> 05:17.350
She just... It's not there.
What're you gonna do ?

05:17.420 --> 05:21.960
Well, me and her,
we got a connection.

05:28.010 --> 05:29.930
Jesus Christ.
Get this fuckin' shit...

05:29.990 --> 05:32.270
- out of my face.
- You should've written to that magazine.

05:32.330 --> 05:34.190
I should've, yeah.

05:34.250 --> 05:37.170
I'm gonna walk outta here. I'm gonna
walk right into a relationship.

05:37.220 --> 05:41.260
And you, my friend,
will walk out with your bus fare.

05:41.320 --> 05:43.270
Searching for
the drunkest skirt in the room.

05:43.340 --> 05:47.050
That's right.
"Morning, gorgeous. More eggnog ?"

05:47.110 --> 05:52.590
- Should've written, Rudy.
You'd have got yourself a girl.

05:52.650 --> 05:55.820
Yeah, should've done
a lot of things.

05:57.710 --> 06:02.320
All I want is just
to make it back to Sidnaw,

06:02.380 --> 06:05.590
sit down for Christmas dinner,

06:05.640 --> 06:08.370
sleep in my old bed,

06:08.430 --> 06:12.110
watch some ball games
with my old man,

06:12.170 --> 06:15.090
eat leftovers for about six months.

06:15.150 --> 06:17.840
I just wanna go home.

06:41.810 --> 06:43.510
Keep the line movin'.

06:43.570 --> 06:46.230
- What's this ?
- Holiday Jell-O.

06:46.290 --> 06:50.070
- What this shit in it ?
- Swallow it and you'll see.

06:50.130 --> 06:53.720
Just so you know,

06:53.780 --> 06:56.820
this man and I are outta here
in two days.

06:56.880 --> 07:00.120
So while we're inhaling
London broil and lobster bisque,

07:00.180 --> 07:04.090
you're still gonna be standing
here smelling up the myster cream fuck.

07:04.150 --> 07:07.280
Who's in prison now ?

07:09.240 --> 07:11.600
Hey, Alamo, how ya doin' ?

07:11.670 --> 07:14.810
Out of solitar ?
Look good. Lose some weight ?

07:16.370 --> 07:18.710
Look, man,
it wasn't me.

07:19.900 --> 07:23.350
- It wasn't me.
- Two days, man. Come on.

07:29.430 --> 07:33.180
Remember how her brother's
a truck driver down there ?

07:33.240 --> 07:35.770
I'm thinkin' he might be able
to get me some work.

07:35.840 --> 07:38.430
What work, security ?

07:38.490 --> 07:41.150
I'm through with that shit.
Ashley's right.

07:41.210 --> 07:45.950
I gotta start doin' somethin'
I got a stake in, get a business goin'.

07:46.040 --> 07:49.690
I don't know, man.
I been in the business world.

07:49.760 --> 07:54.200
Hot-wiring cars, Rudy, does not
qualify you as a small business.

07:54.270 --> 07:56.510
"Chop-shop consultant"
doesn't work on a resume.

07:56.580 --> 07:59.870
I always wanted to be
the boss of something, ya know?

07:59.960 --> 08:02.720
Have people working for me.

08:05.750 --> 08:08.830
Man, what's wrong with you ?

08:08.890 --> 08:11.680
Monsters... in the gelatin.

08:11.750 --> 08:14.720
- It's just a roach, Zook.
- Yeah, it's protein. It's good for ya.

08:14.780 --> 08:19.520
- Monsters... in the gelatin !
- Calm down.

08:19.620 --> 08:24.350
There are monsters
in the gelatin !

08:24.450 --> 08:28.260
Monsters... in the gelatin !

08:28.320 --> 08:30.760
Look at this shit !

08:30.810 --> 08:32.390
Hey ! Jesus !

08:32.450 --> 08:35.610
- Sit down !
- Son of a bitch !

08:36.710 --> 08:40.000
You eat this shit !

08:40.070 --> 08:44.200
- Get down, don't move.
- Stay out of it, Rudy !

08:45.980 --> 08:50.020
You want
some fucking monsters ?

08:51.620 --> 08:53.350
Two days, man.

08:53.410 --> 08:57.570
Fuck !

09:01.540 --> 09:03.240
Don't move !

09:04.580 --> 09:06.470
We had nothing to do with it!

09:09.770 --> 09:11.850
Rudy, watch out !

09:23.270 --> 09:26.310
Cassidy's down ! Cassidy's stabbed!

09:26.380 --> 09:29.610
- I gotta be there.
- Oh, my God !

09:29.670 --> 09:31.560
- Rudy, Ashley.
- You're gonna be all right.

09:31.630 --> 09:35.370
- Hold on, hold on. Guard ! Jesus, guards !
- Ashley's gonna be there.

09:35.430 --> 09:38.160
- Nick, you gotta...
- Gotta be...

09:38.210 --> 09:40.580
Guard ! Guards !

09:40.650 --> 09:42.820
Jesus Christ.

09:44.430 --> 09:48.580
- Nick. Nick ! Nick !
- Get him outta here now!

10:03.210 --> 10:06.670
Well, at least
he won't be comin' back.

10:09.000 --> 10:14.030
You need some company tonight, Rudy,
you just give me a holler.

10:19.150 --> 10:23.120
You gonna take that from him ?
You gonna take that shit, Rudy ?

11:15.440 --> 11:19.060
Open outer gate.

11:26.390 --> 11:29.850
Your world and welcome to it,
you dumb fucks.

11:29.940 --> 11:32.510
Don't be a stranger now.
We'll keep the lights on for ya.

11:32.600 --> 11:35.420
Over here !

11:57.180 --> 11:59.390
Over here.
Hey, how you doin' ?

12:22.370 --> 12:26.210
"And all that gets me
through the day, is to close my eyes...

12:26.300 --> 12:30.110
"and imagine holding you,
kissing you,

12:30.210 --> 12:33.760
touching you."

12:33.860 --> 12:38.590
Don't do it, Rudy.
Don't you fucking do it !

12:47.520 --> 12:50.470
Jesus Christ.

13:22.180 --> 13:24.800
Are you Ashley ?

13:29.380 --> 13:31.400
I'm Nick !

13:54.920 --> 13:57.290
Look, Ashley, I'm sorry.

13:57.390 --> 13:59.940
I was scared that
I was gonna walk out there,

14:00.040 --> 14:03.010
and you were gonna take one look
at me and just... turn around.

14:03.110 --> 14:06.030
I was scared I was walkin'
into heartache.

14:06.130 --> 14:09.800
All those letters, those words,
and you have a picture in your mind.

14:11.370 --> 14:16.110
I was scared you'd see me,
and I just wouldn't be that...

14:16.170 --> 14:18.410
picture that you had
in your mind.

14:18.510 --> 14:22.380
I figured you walked outta there
and saw my clothes or something,

14:22.480 --> 14:25.140
and you just walked
right the other way.

14:25.230 --> 14:28.940
- You know, maybe you saw my coat or my hair...
- Hey, I like your coat !

14:29.030 --> 14:31.240
Maybe you...

14:32.780 --> 14:35.890
Maybe you saw me and I didn't...

14:35.990 --> 14:39.690
Ashley, no. That was me.

14:43.980 --> 14:47.410
I thought you said you,
had curly hair.

14:47.510 --> 14:50.060
I do. It's ver curly.

14:50.160 --> 14:53.580
When it gets long, it's really curly.
But I cut it short.

14:53.680 --> 14:57.170
I can grow it out again, if you want.
I can get it pretty bushy.

14:57.260 --> 15:00.590
No ! No, no, no.

15:00.690 --> 15:03.830
I want you to be
who you wanna be.

15:03.920 --> 15:06.090
Do that again.

15:06.190 --> 15:08.630
What ?

15:08.730 --> 15:10.290
Smile like that.

15:13.460 --> 15:16.150
Come on.
One more time.

15:22.030 --> 15:25.750
God, I have been dreaming
about that smile...

15:25.840 --> 15:28.310
for so long,

15:28.410 --> 15:30.770
Ashley Mercer.

15:35.220 --> 15:39.480
You're better than the pictures
in my mind, Nick.

15:42.430 --> 15:44.690
You're real !

16:50.880 --> 16:53.050
Can I ask you somethin' ?

16:53.120 --> 16:55.970
Is this the first time you ever
done somethin' like this ?

16:57.630 --> 17:00.220
You, look at you.

17:00.290 --> 17:03.420
So pretty, sweet.

17:03.490 --> 17:07.589
Why were you writing to a guy,
some con, you don't even know ?

17:07.650 --> 17:11.390
- I told you, Nick. Remember ?
- Tell me again.

17:16.480 --> 17:20.450
All the guys
I've ever been with,

17:20.510 --> 17:23.720
they never wanted
to get to know me.

17:26.410 --> 17:30.150
Who I am... inside.

17:30.210 --> 17:33.760
They just wanted to...
get inside.

17:36.010 --> 17:38.700
A guy like you, Nick.

17:38.750 --> 17:43.110
God, I mean, six months
before you could even touch my face.

17:44.610 --> 17:46.690
I figure
a guy like that...

17:46.760 --> 17:50.560
is gonna have to work
to get to know me some other way.

18:02.820 --> 18:05.870
But when I read
what you wrote to me,

18:08.390 --> 18:12.300
"Here's a guy they say is a criminal,
but he's not.

18:12.360 --> 18:14.220
"Just protected his girl.

18:14.280 --> 18:19.430
"Somebody got killed,
but he's not a killer...

18:20.870 --> 18:26.060
"'cause he did what he had to do
to save somebody.

18:26.130 --> 18:29.830
And the world just
didn't see it that way."

18:29.900 --> 18:32.170
State of Michigan, anyway.

18:32.230 --> 18:35.500
You wrote me
some wonderful things.

18:35.560 --> 18:38.860
It wasn't all me, you know.

18:38.920 --> 18:41.490
It was all you.

18:41.550 --> 18:45.960
The guy I was in with, you know,
he helped me with some of the romantic stuff.

18:46.030 --> 18:48.020
He's a good guy, actually.
You'd like him.

18:48.070 --> 18:53.200
I'm talkin' about the heart,
not the words.

18:53.260 --> 18:55.890
Yeah, well,

18:55.950 --> 18:59.180
some of the heart
might've been his too.

18:59.250 --> 19:01.100
Yeah ?

19:09.580 --> 19:13.610
You should've signed his name,
then he'd be here right now.

19:35.350 --> 19:38.290
Merry Christmas !

19:38.360 --> 19:41.650
Merry Christmas, Santa !

19:41.720 --> 19:44.150
Provisions, Nick.
Provisions.

19:44.210 --> 19:46.320
Come here.
You need a coat.

19:46.390 --> 19:50.390
No boyfriend of mine is gonna walk around
in a negative five degree wind chill...

19:50.450 --> 19:52.340
without a good-looking goddamn coat.

19:52.400 --> 19:56.280
But you already got me all this stuff.
I didn't get you anything.

19:56.340 --> 20:00.080
Nick, you got out.
You're here.

20:00.150 --> 20:02.520
You're my Christmas.

20:02.580 --> 20:04.880
It's $ 200, Ash.

20:04.950 --> 20:09.660
I know !
But you forget where I work.

20:09.720 --> 20:14.970
- Beauty and fragrances.
- Yep. Fifty percent off, my friend.

20:25.310 --> 20:27.680
Just till the holidays, Nick.

20:27.730 --> 20:30.040
We'll let her have her holidays,

20:30.110 --> 20:32.000
then we'll tell her.

20:49.690 --> 20:52.640
I'm gonna tell them not to bother us
for the rest of the year.

20:52.700 --> 20:57.590
When I get back in that room, you better
be wearing nothing but a candy cane.

21:04.030 --> 21:07.770
I have no gifts to bring

21:12.450 --> 21:16.550
A gift to give a King

21:16.600 --> 21:20.220
I've got a girl...

21:20.290 --> 21:22.140
Hi, Nick.

21:43.870 --> 21:45.930
Ah, shit !

21:50.150 --> 21:52.710
I oweyou a drink !

21:56.260 --> 21:58.120
Welcome home, Nick.

22:01.830 --> 22:03.790
Look, man, you don't know me.

22:03.840 --> 22:07.270
I know ya.

22:07.340 --> 22:09.220
- I know you real well.
- You can't.

22:09.290 --> 22:11.240
The hell I can't.

22:11.300 --> 22:13.250
- Watch out, baby,
- Ashley !

22:13.320 --> 22:15.790
I'm bringin' in the tree !

22:28.080 --> 22:32.230
Looks like somebody's
been havin' some fun.

22:35.790 --> 22:39.080
Hey, sis, happy holidays.

22:39.150 --> 22:41.350
No ! You bastard ! No !

22:41.420 --> 22:44.990
- Take it easy. Don't hurt her.
- Right. Sorry, Monster.

22:47.720 --> 22:50.410
So,

22:50.480 --> 22:54.800
this is the guy you've been waitin' for,
the man of your dreams.

22:54.860 --> 22:56.880
Gabriel, what are you doing ?

22:56.940 --> 23:00.680
- I read a lot about you, Nick.
- Gabriel, what are you doing here ?

23:00.750 --> 23:04.230
I read you're a man
of some knowledge.

23:04.300 --> 23:07.020
- Gabriel.
- A man of some travels.

23:07.090 --> 23:12.340
Look, man, I'm not him. Whatever you
want from Nick, you got the wrong guy.

23:12.400 --> 23:17.960
- Nick ?
- I'm sorry, Ashley. I'm sorry.

23:19.690 --> 23:23.700
No ! No !

23:23.760 --> 23:27.990
- Who are you now ?
- I'm not him, man !

23:28.050 --> 23:31.210
- She just thinks I'm Nick. I'm not him.
- Put him in the truck.

23:31.280 --> 23:33.130
Wait a minute !
I was in the joint with him.

23:33.200 --> 23:35.760
That's how I knew about him and her.
I took his place.

23:35.820 --> 23:40.280
- You what ?
- Okay. I got out. Nick didn't.

23:40.330 --> 23:44.240
I knew about her letters,
and Jesus Christ, man,

23:44.310 --> 23:46.860
whatever you want from Nick,
I'm not him, okay ?

23:46.930 --> 23:49.170
I just... I wanted to be.

23:53.840 --> 23:55.890
You're not Nick Cassidy ?

23:55.960 --> 23:58.960
No, man, I just shared his cell.

23:59.030 --> 24:01.910
But you were saying you were.

24:01.980 --> 24:03.860
Yeah.

24:03.920 --> 24:06.810
So you could get with my sister.

24:06.870 --> 24:08.750
Yeah.

24:08.820 --> 24:13.170
- So you could get down her chimney.
- Yeah.

24:14.750 --> 24:17.340
And you think tellin' me,
that's gonna help your cause.

24:19.740 --> 24:22.230
No !

24:22.290 --> 24:24.400
No ! No !

24:24.470 --> 24:28.150
- Is this him ?
- Please don't hurt him, Gabriel. Don't !

24:28.220 --> 24:31.930
- Is this the fucker you been writin' all year ?
- Don't ! Please, don't.

24:31.990 --> 24:34.770
- Is this Nick Cassidy ?
- Yes !

24:34.840 --> 24:37.630
Yes !

24:37.690 --> 24:41.490
Well, he better learn
to give you some respect.

24:43.000 --> 24:47.100
- Get her outta here.
- No !

24:49.050 --> 24:50.900
No !

24:53.050 --> 24:55.030
Man, they got a shitload
of cookies.

24:55.100 --> 24:56.660
Take 'em.

24:57.880 --> 24:59.830
What about the tree ?

24:59.900 --> 25:03.620
- You want the tree ?
- Yeah.

25:14.940 --> 25:17.690
I read your letters, convict.

25:20.730 --> 25:23.780
Don't play no reindeer games
with me.

25:34.200 --> 25:36.160
He read your letters.

25:36.220 --> 25:39.720
One day I wasn't there
and he came in.

25:39.770 --> 25:43.040
Jane tried to stop him,
but he read your letters.

25:43.110 --> 25:45.820
What letters ?

25:45.890 --> 25:48.550
He knows you worked
at that casino.

25:54.370 --> 25:57.820
What ?
Oh, my God, you set him up !

25:57.890 --> 26:00.220
No, no, I didn't. I didn't.

26:00.290 --> 26:03.140
When did you decide
to do it, Ash ?

26:03.200 --> 26:07.370
After which one of his letters ?
What, the for tieth, fiftieth ? The first ? What ?

26:07.430 --> 26:09.700
- No, Nick, you're not...
- Look, I'm not Nick !

26:09.770 --> 26:13.060
Okay ? You thought
you'd fuck him over ?

26:13.130 --> 26:15.460
Ah, shit ! Guess what ?
He fucked you !

26:15.530 --> 26:19.080
Because I never worked in any casino,
and I can't help you because I'm not him !

26:19.140 --> 26:22.310
- No, you don't understand. I love you !
- Jesus...

26:22.370 --> 26:25.860
- Christ!
- Hey, hey, watch your mouth. It's Christmas.

26:25.930 --> 26:29.000
Listen to me. Listen to me.

26:29.070 --> 26:32.260
My brother has killed people.
I know this.

26:32.330 --> 26:35.080
You don't know him. You don't know
what he's capable of. He will kill you.

26:35.140 --> 26:38.280
If you keep telling him
that you're not you, he will kill you.

26:38.340 --> 26:42.340
