legislate a second such gift-giving holiday.

26:54.350 --> 26:57.830
Create, say, a Christmas Two,
late May or early June,

26:57.900 --> 27:00.080
to further stimulate growth.

27:00.140 --> 27:03.880
Ever since you been goin' to night school,
you been giving me headaches, Jumpy.

27:03.950 --> 27:07.430
Christmas Two.

27:16.070 --> 27:18.350
Just...

27:23.530 --> 27:27.920
"My sweet, sexy Ashy-lashy.

27:29.290 --> 27:31.310
"I have been dreaming of you
constantly,

27:31.380 --> 27:33.740
"and knowing you are out there
makes these walls...

27:33.810 --> 27:37.770
"not seem so close
or so strong or so cold.

27:39.120 --> 27:42.130
"Someday I'm gonna take you
up by Lake Superior.

27:42.190 --> 27:46.550
"Before I went in,
before goddamn Millie,

27:46.610 --> 27:48.760
"I used to work up
at this casino,

27:48.810 --> 27:50.990
